    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-sim-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo propagation confirms the 95th-percentile hemolysis index band remains below the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion across the full CPB operating envelope. Output comparison yields NIA = 0.91 with no systematic bias. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory decision that the CFD model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Assessment accepted at Medium assurance level.",
